place_brief_desc: Hub of fashion, design, and diamonds.
place_longer_desc: The second-largest city in Belgium and a major port, Antwerp is a hub of fashion, design, and diamonds. Why not visit the Cathedral of Our Lady or be equally as awestruck by the Centraal Station. The Diamond Museum is worth a nosey, as is the trendy Zuid district. You can also shop for some of the best clothes and jewellery in Europe - apparently (I didn’t notice them last time I was there but …).
